  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "高山是瑪督烏瓦爾的故鄉，擁有豐富的農特產。春季有高山草莓和桂竹筍；夏季有桃子和李子；秋季有番茄；冬季有柑橘、甜柿、生薑等。",
      "ab": "pinamuwan na itaal nku’ Matu’uwal ku’ ibabawiq ka ragiyax. payux ku’ pinumuwa’ naha’. tikay ka gabagan ga, kiya a ihuk na ragiyax, balku ru gabagan ga, kiya a qaym, pilikaway. tikay ka qamisan ga kiya a a’utaq, qamisan la ga kiya a iyuk, ralu’ ru qurip.",
